dc:description: Information about friends of the individual in a social network. Includes aspects of friendships such as years together or nature of friendship.
dc:creator: Elmar Kiesling, Harshvardhan J. Pandit, Fajar Ekaputra

rdfs:label: Group Membership
dc:description: Information about groups the individual is included or associated with in a social network
dc:creator: Elmar Kiesling, Harshvardhan J. Pandit, Fajar Ekaputra

rdfs:label: Device Based
dc:description: Information about a device that an individual uses for personal use (even part-time or with others)
dc:creator: Elmar Kiesling, Harshvardhan J. Pandit, Fajar Ekaputra

rdfs:label: Location
dc:description: Information about an individual’s location
dc:creator: Elmar Kiesling, Harshvardhan J. Pandit, Fajar Ekaputra

rdfs:label: Contact
dc:description: Information that can be used for contacting an individual e.g. email address or phone number
dc:creator: Elmar Kiesling, Harshvardhan J. Pandit, Fajar Ekaputra

rdfs:label: Credit
dc:description: Information about an individual’s reputation with regards to money
dc:creator: Elmar Kiesling, Harshvardhan J. Pandit, Fajar Ekaputra

rdfs:label: Income
dc:description: Information about financial income e.g. for individual or household or family
dc:creator: Elmar Kiesling, Harshvardhan J. Pandit, Fajar Ekaputra

rdfs:label: Loan Record
dc:description: Information about loans provided or related to the individual
dc:creator: Elmar Kiesling, Harshvardhan J. Pandit, Fajar Ekaputra

rdfs:label: Purchase
dc:description: Information about purchases such as items bought e.g. grocery or clothing
dc:creator: Elmar Kiesling, Harshvardhan J. Pandit, Fajar Ekaputra

rdfs:label: Purchases and Spending Habit
dc:description: Information about analysis of purchases made and money spent expressed as a habit e.g. monthly shopping trends
dc:creator: Elmar Kiesling, Harshvardhan J. Pandit, Fajar Ekaputra

rdfs:label: Sale
dc:description: Information about sales e.g. selling of goods or services
dc:creator: Elmar Kiesling, Harshvardhan J. Pandit, Fajar Ekaputra

rdfs:label: Tax
dc:description: Information about financial tax e.g. tax records or tax due
dc:creator: Elmar Kiesling, Harshvardhan J. Pandit, Fajar Ekaputra

rdfs:label: Transaction
dc:description: Information about financial transactions e.g. bank transfers
dc:creator: Elmar Kiesling, Harshvardhan J. Pandit, Fajar Ekaputra
